{"tid":286198,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「體操濱崎步」：開腿就一堆喀擦聲　田中理惠抱怨都愛拍她私處跟猙獰表情","createTime":"2017-06-16T12:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T16:30:59.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"144cf32ee7e4436da6a0593f65695da63b10bb0d","tid":286198,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T12:02:08.000Z","msg":"擁有力與美的前日本體操選手田中理惠，因外貌甜美可愛，被稱為「體操界濱崎步」，不過近日她卻在在節目上自爆，過去參加比賽只要做開腿動作，就會有一堆記者拍下她的姿勢和下體，讓她很不舒服。<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/06/14/937943-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F937943-XXL.jpg&h=c67ed8a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲田中理惠節目自爆，每次做開腿動作就會被記者狂拍下體。<br />\n<br />\n據日本《Livedoor》報導，田中理惠參加2013年退役，近日參加日本富士台節目有關「優秀女子運動旅行」訪談，問到田中理惠參加2012年倫敦奧運「有無走光經驗」，起初她表示「沒有」，不過卻猶豫了一下改說「如果有，應該是下面」，並解釋，比賽時每次只要做開腿動作，就會聽到比平常要多的快門喀擦聲，而且不僅是平衡木，在其他的項目也是如此，「其實我們在場上都聽得一清二楚」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/A9Ru8LQ7jrRv31banw2KKA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant_TW/News/YahooOmg/20130128163532_sakutmc_935427.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FA9Ru8LQ7jrRv31banw2KKA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDUwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant_TW%2FNews%2FYahooOmg%2F20130128163532_sakutmc_935427.jpg&h=33ca5506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n田中理惠還抱怨，記者們除了愛拍下體，也特愛拍她比賽中表情猙獰的樣子，「每次都把我最醜的照片刻意放在最明顯的位置」，讓她感覺十分無奈。因為外型酷似歌手濱崎步而出名的田中理惠，在2010年到2012年間為日本體操國家代表隊選手，曾於亞運拿下3面獎牌，才貌兼具的她2013年因腰部健康問題而退役，但退役後依然十分有人氣。<br />\n<br />\n▼田中理惠抱怨，記者每次都愛拍她私處跟猙獰表情。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/que-11159302396-297x300.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fque-11159302396-297x300.png&h=058281ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2017-06-13/656/20170613003895.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2017-06-13%2F656%2F20170613003895.jpg&h=4f3f58c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae236f67faa87be95394cdb587411881f457adc0","tid":286198,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T12:06:43.000Z","msg":"唔樣衰都唔影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d96800480b7d1a01cec6ad532c56e2eb8bc8e7","tid":286198,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T12:16:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0cb823c93b16eb626d3af9799b8fbab32a6f4708","tid":286198,"uid":5945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"張圖係田中直樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}